# NOTE: data/ is deliberately committed (datasets + full call transcripts).
# Vendoring raw data in-repo isn't usual practice, but this is a small (~6MB),
# self-contained research artifact where the transcripts ARE the result — keeping
# them next to the code makes the study reproducible and auditable in one clone.
# Keep it simple: no LFS, no external bucket. .env stays ignored (secrets only).
